  "detailed_description": "PixageFX Studio is the flagship of the PixageFX family. With PixageFX Studio you can turn photos, videos and animated GIFs into pixel art, oil paints, abstract paintings, cartoons, comics, sketches and more. In addition, thanks to its parametric structure, you can perform transform operations and much more that you may need every day.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPixageFX Studio has hundreds of modules. Each module is completely parametric. Just add a module to your project for the action you want to do.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFor detailed information about PixageFX Studio, please visit our website. Please see the PixageFX Comparison chart for differences with other PixageFX family members.",
  "about_the_game": "PixageFX Studio is the flagship of the PixageFX family. With PixageFX Studio you can turn photos, videos and animated GIFs into pixel art, oil paints, abstract paintings, cartoons, comics, sketches and more. In addition, thanks to its parametric structure, you can perform transform operations and much more that you may need every day.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPixageFX Studio has hundreds of modules. Each module is completely parametric. Just add a module to your project for the action you want to do.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFor detailed information about PixageFX Studio, please visit our website. Please see the PixageFX Comparison chart for differences with other PixageFX family members.",
